	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello,
<br />
<br />I have a 60Hz modded Mega Drive and PAL SNES. Since the cpu clock speeds of the PAL Mega Drive and the PAL SNES are slightly lower than their NTSC counterparts, I was wondering if this will result in more (noticeably) slowdown when running US/JAP Games in 60Hz mode in contrast to running them on a Genesis or US SNES.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


